column2: SELECT t.objid , t.thingid, t.ndetect,t.ra,t.dec, t.thingid, t.ndetect,t.ra,t.dec,d.objid,p.mjd,p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.err_u,p.err_g,p.err_r,p.err_i,p.err_z FROM thingIndex t ,dbo.fgetNearByObjEq(#,#,#) n JOIN detectionindex AS d ON t.thingid = d.thingid JOIN photoobjall AS p ON p.objid = d.objid  where t.objid = n.objid
